    <div class="mini-card mini-card-6266 col-12 col-sm-6 col-md-4"><div class="mini-card-title"><span>Felicia Hawkins</span></div><div class="views-field views-field-field-staff-mugshot"><div class="field-content"></div></div><div class="mini-card-subtitle"><div>Senior Legislative and Public Affairs Specialist</div></div><div class="more-link"><a href="/who-we-are/office-inspector-general/felicia-hawkins" hreflang="en">Learn More</a></div></div>

    </div>
  
          </div>
</span></h3></dd><dt>Press Releases</dt><dd><p>DFC OIG press releases highlight our operational, audit, and investigative work. In addition, we also re-post relevant U.S. Department of Justice and other international press releases where the OIG has jurisdiction and/or was a partner in the investigation.</p><p><div class="page-oig-reports view view-reports view-id-reports view-display-id-block_4 js-view-dom-id-ed3720c2a3bc2dbddea064fb247464ae340ed889fe84ac8ae7433f1150322815">
  
    
        <div class="view-filters form-group">
      <form class="views-exposed-form bef-exposed-form" data-bef-auto-submit-full-form="" data-bef-auto-submit="" data-bef-auto-submit-delay="500" data-drupal-selector="views-exposed-form-reports-block-4" action="/oig" method="get" id="views-exposed-form-reports-block-4" accept-charset="UTF-8">
